Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.71,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that what attracted you to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.71,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she{\i1} needed{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:33.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I could be me...with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:38.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only truth I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...was when I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you tho hear that.  I need....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:45.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and understand where I'm coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:49.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.74,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...There's any hope of saving our marriage....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what my life had become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant assembly line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:40.10,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a series of same actions repeated day in, and day out, for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.84,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[alarm rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:58.42,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[alarm rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.71,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you better get up.  You're gonna be late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I never questioned what I was doing or where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just moved blindly through life from point A to point B.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:23.84,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,A slave to monotony and predictability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that life didn't have to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:37.22,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it wasn't some giant inevitability that marriage equated to boredom and complacency...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:41.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I saw how vibrant, authentic, honest, and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:45.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...other married people seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:51.77,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Really curious about double-penetration with Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Vickie had been my friend and coworker for 6 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was as free as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...refreshingly unapologetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:11.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...in who she was...and blissfully married to the love of her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.82,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like to say a few words before I lose everyone to the effects of booze...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:47.65,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...weed or whatever other drugs you might've struggled in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.65,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,17 years ago....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.65,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I met Vickie McDaniels...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.00,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the most incredibly beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:04:00.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and insanely honest...and emotionally crazy women I've ever met in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:05.22,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,3 weeks later...we were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said we...were too young...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...that we'd be divorced within a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:16.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother even suggested we have the marriage annulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she was the girl for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:27.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you for 17 of the best years of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:32.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You love me...love me for who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:35.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...accepting me for who I'm not without any judgment or criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:43.37,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the 17 years of proving everyone they're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:49.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!  Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:55.92,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why he thinks the relationship is so much better than everyone else's just because....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.31,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...they knew each other for 3 weeks before they got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.20,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That was exactly his point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:11.00,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at us.  We only dated for 3 weeks and we're still together 17 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We're better...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that is so phony, Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.91,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to show how happy they are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:25.16,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're happy together, you don't have to prove it to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They are kind of like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.97,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know them better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for coming tonight.  It means so much to both of us to have you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have missed it for the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! You two look so happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have another cigarette, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were trying to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I bum a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Cool.  Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.81,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,3 weeks can turn into 17 years real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.79,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's quite the story brook romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's just incredible, they're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.28,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...defying all the odds and proving the naysayers wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very Romeo and Juliet without all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...mutual suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's my aunt actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.45,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:43.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually worked with her for 6 years.  She's a great lady.  She's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Are you the uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the niece who does amazing photography?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:54.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!  Did she say amazing?  She's really exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I'm her niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:59.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it.  It's really amazing stuff?  Wow, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:03.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been going to school now for a couple of years trying to perfect my technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...It's getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmmm.  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:13.07,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get any interesting shots in there?  Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.07,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:26.41,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just so much more going on with you than you're projecting in that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.41,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot in your lines right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just zoning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No the camera doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been photographing people for years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, like 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been doing anything for years yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:47.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've been shooting since I was 15.  So that's 10 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.80,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh, I'm Mimi by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around.  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.47,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel horrible about the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:37.10,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop beating yourself up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not a fan of Vickie and her husband but uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't need you to like them.  It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  I don't feel horrible about hating Vickie and Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:50.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel horrible about...I've been right all along about their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:09:00.07,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw them...with another woman...in their bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  A three way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:07.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of me!  It was like a circus act or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.96,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,During the party?  Yes, at the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:16.47,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the master bathroom peeing, waiting for you to finish your cigarette....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:20.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of the sudden I hear a noise.  So I went to peak out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:24.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw Roy with another woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...which I thought, he was having an affair....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...which would be hilarious, given the fact that he's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...in love with Vickie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.00,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They're touching each other and groping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.74,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:40.27,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:44.18,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they start heading toward the bathroom that I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,So I freaked out!  Jumped in the shower and shut the curtain....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and just hoped they wouldn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Vickie walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.86,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm thinking that she's going to yell at Roy for cheating on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But she joined in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,This was clearly a threesome they had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:55.86,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:31.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:05.20,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Anniversary, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:08.57,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you.  Love you, amazing guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:12.79,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.62,0:24:48.67,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.07,0:24:55.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.60,0:24:58.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No!  It was horrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.62,0:25:01.33,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you see what I mean when I say phony?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:03.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sexual deviants, Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.99,0:25:05.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:09.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual deviants can be happily married.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:13.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hope they sanitize the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:15.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean they had people at their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.23,0:25:17.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't he have waited until everyone left?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.63,0:25:19.26,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "passion" Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.26,0:25:20.53,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,  Spontaneity....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.53,0:25:23.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you what...after 17 years of marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:25.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.05,0:25:27.79,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:44.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.05,0:25:48.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,God!  Is she okay?  No. She's completely scarred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.40,0:25:50.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,She should have just said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:52.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's too afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.88,0:25:55.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  That we were going to ask her to join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.12,0:25:58.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean....it wouldn't have been completely out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:00.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It might loosen her up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.69,0:26:03.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no loosening Christine up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.60,0:26:05.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.60,0:26:08.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as she's happy being that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.07,0:26:10.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth was...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.69,0:26:13.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't know if Christine was happy being that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.73,0:26:15.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,For as long as I had known her...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.73,0:26:18.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...she had been straight and narrow in every aspect of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.89,0:26:21.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And no amount of loosening her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:23.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...will seem to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.01,0:26:25.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought her new lingerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:27.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.66,0:26:32.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Sex toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.55,0:26:38.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.09,0:26:42.34,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Even attempted spontaneous foreplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.54,0:26:47.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.06,0:26:49.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No!  Come on!  No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:51.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Drew!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:54.37,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I began to wonder if the root of our problems had more to do with my...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.37,0:27:00.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...inability to vocalize...those problems than they did her inability to unwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.38,0:27:02.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't I just tell her how I felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.95,0:27:05.31,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,So there I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.67,0:27:08.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Going through the motions of life like a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.08,0:27:09.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Craving change.
