Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.72,0:55:52.81,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.81,0:55:57.37,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.46,0:56:02.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the first time in, it felt like forever, I was actually living.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.83,0:56:04.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just getting by.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.94,0:56:17.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.99,0:56:19.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know I'm happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.67,0:56:22.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's permeating through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.90,0:56:27.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.06,0:56:32.07,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace it!  It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.07,0:56:34.07,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.40,0:56:40.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in my life, I had a relationship that was both emotionally and physically fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.46,0:56:42.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.46,0:56:47.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I could share absolutely anything with Mimi without fear of being criticized or judged...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.66,0:56:49.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from Vickie....
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.66,0:56:51.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was the most open person I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.66,0:56:53.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Wise beyond her years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:57.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend to me.  Not just a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.11,0:56:59.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We laughed often.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.54,0:57:02.39,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Encouraged one another's hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.39,0:57:05.95,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoyed a sense of freedom I'd never known with Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.82,0:57:23.03,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But as with every affair...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.03,0:57:26.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality rears its ugly head at one point or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.77,0:57:28.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'll figure out a way to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.76,0:57:32.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.  I just...really want to know what it's like to wake up next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.75,0:57:33.95,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.95,0:57:37.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your roommate mind?  Does ... know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.09,0:57:41.22,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he knows and he thinks it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.22,0:57:42.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.51,0:57:45.92,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't think I want to subject ourselves to that sort of negativity right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.43,0:57:51.82,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  I will get ourselves a hotel room in the next week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.82,0:57:53.82,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.82,0:57:54.95,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.95,0:57:58.24,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit frustrated myself, so....
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.24,0:58:02.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I got to go.  So I'll call you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.70,0:58:04.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.  Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.66,0:58:06.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.55,0:58:19.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you talking to just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.25,0:58:20.56,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.56,0:58:23.57,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost midnight.  Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.57,0:58:24.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Vickie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.43,0:58:27.19,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to keep you up taking the call in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.39,0:58:30.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you talking to Vickie about getting a hotel room?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.30,0:58:32.10,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're taking a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.10,0:58:35.86,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's talking about saving the company money, staying with her sister, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.86,0:58:38.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...We'll just get a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.32,0:58:40.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.  When is the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.12,0:58:43.57,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for a few weeks if we take the trip at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.81,0:58:51.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And suddenly, all the guilt I thought I was immune to...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.12,0:58:53.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...had returned full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.33,0:58:55.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Blind to Christine felt wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.62,0:58:58.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sick about it.  But I was terrified to...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.69,0:59:00.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...to come clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.69,0:59:05.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrified to admit that a relationship that I had spent nearly 20 years of my life in...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.12,0:59:07.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...had somehow failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.34,0:59:19.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Living more honestly had ironically propelled me into the affair to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.83,0:59:21.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Now here I was.  Lying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.14,0:59:23.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.83,0:59:26.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Voicemails...emails...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.29,0:59:28.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid to admit what I really needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.29,0:59:32.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...in an effort to protect what I no longer wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.84,0:59:35.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do something so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.15,0:59:39.39,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know that it's wrong.  But I can't help how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.39,0:59:42.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad at me for saying this....but....
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.02,0:59:45.24,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...married men never leave their wives, Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.14,0:59:51.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think that he's in love with you don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.23,0:59:52.91,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.91,0:59:54.50,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi?  Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.50,1:00:00.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I sound like every other stupid girl that falls in love with a married man, but this is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.46,1:00:05.26,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Every woman that falls in love with a married man thinks that she's somehow different.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.26,1:00:08.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not any different.  You're a walking cliché.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.13,1:00:10.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You're half his age for chrissake!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.62,1:00:11.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.63,1:00:13.37,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never what anyone thinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.37,1:00:18.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get too wrapped up in thinking that you have some future with him, cause...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.21,1:00:20.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't.  He's never gonna leave his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.21,1:00:22.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.82,1:00:25.91,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi shared her concerns with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.91,1:00:30.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fear was that I wasn't in this for the long haul.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.61,1:00:35.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And as much as I tried to convince her that my intentions were sincere...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.15,1:00:38.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...my actions began to fall short.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.02,1:00:41.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry Mimi, I'm gonna have to take a rain check for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.54,1:00:42.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.54,1:00:46.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Christine's car battery is dead and AAA hasn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.59,1:00:48.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.59,1:00:50.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.89,1:00:55.14,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your birthday.  Oh god, I feel so terrible about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.14,1:00:57.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.  We can celebrate next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.66,1:01:01.53,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.  I'm going to make this up to you ten-fold.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.53,1:01:03.53,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.07,1:01:26.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.55,1:01:31.84,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't sustain two independent relationships without one of them getting the brunt of the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.84,1:01:34.14,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be in two places at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.14,1:01:36.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter how badly I wanted to be with her...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.73,1:01:39.86,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I still had an obligation to Christine and our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.38,1:01:45.16,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Missing Mimi's birthday was the first of many events I couldn't meet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.55,1:01:48.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But none more important than her gallery opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.92,1:01:53.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,None of my teachers are coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.73,1:02:00.06,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one photography teacher and a journalism teacher....and a couple of friends...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.06,1:02:02.47,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be there, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.47,1:02:05.95,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely!  I promise I'll be there.  Wouldn't miss it for the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.95,1:02:10.74,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, cause I know we can't hold hands or be affectionate...but...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.74,1:02:14.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would mean so much to me if you were there...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.44,1:02:15.77,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,For my first big show.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.76,1:02:16.65,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.86,1:02:20.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be there after...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.80,1:02:22.96,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...for our celebration.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.80,1:02:26.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi....?  Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.68,1:02:30.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you tiny girl...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.58,1:02:46.84,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.20,1:02:50.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.90,1:02:52.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.62,1:02:58.35,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.35,1:03:00.16,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they think he's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.45,1:03:03.72,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I might head up there this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.72,1:03:05.72,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course, of course!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.95,1:03:09.41,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Drew, I'd really like it if you'd come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.70,1:03:12.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I might fall apart on this one if I do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.98,1:03:15.31,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.31,1:03:16.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.63,1:03:19.45,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Christine had admitted to needing me emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.11,1:03:22.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though the timing couldn't have been worse...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.85,1:03:24.42,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I say "no"?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.72,1:03:32.94,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.19,1:03:38.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just hanging this on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.55,1:03:40.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.55,1:03:43.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my favorite one of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.11,1:03:45.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.62,1:03:47.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.30,1:03:54.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Christine's father had a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.68,1:03:57.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.00,1:03:59.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry is he okay?  Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.90,1:04:01.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.53,1:04:02.80,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,He's OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.80,1:04:05.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna drive up there tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.60,1:04:09.45,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.56,1:04:14.81,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.13,1:04:20.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...if I could be here to support you...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.25,1:04:22.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...your big night...I would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.76,1:04:25.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[Sighs]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.05,1:04:27.60,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.37,1:04:33.81,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing work though.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.81,1:04:36.52,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everybody's gonna be so impressed with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.98,1:04:42.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it's funny...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.78,1:04:47.24,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this entire year, I've never once asked you about your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.63,1:04:50.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that...I could be your escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.25,1:04:54.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That if I pretended that she didn't exist then I could pretend that I wasn't just your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.86,1:04:58.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just my mistress...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.05,1:05:02.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,By anyone else's definition that is exactly what I am!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.12,1:05:04.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad cheated on my mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.25,1:05:10.10,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I never told you that because it devastated her.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.74,1:05:12.81,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what that did to somebody!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.81,1:05:16.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw how much that hurt, and I swore I would never do that to somebody!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.19,1:05:18.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.75,1:05:21.35,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know look at me...I'm just a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.23,1:05:24.16,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,This is different Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.05,1:05:26.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it different?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.44,1:05:28.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean really!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.44,1:05:30.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.44,1:05:32.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know deep down in my gut...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.40,1:05:35.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I can't feel for anyone...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.76,1:05:37.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...the way that I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.33,1:05:40.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understood his direction for life...it got too boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.98,1:05:42.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.98,1:05:44.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.63,1:05:48.24,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were truly unhappy with her...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.24,1:05:51.67,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what we really had meant something then why would you stay married?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.67,1:05:54.34,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I was married to Christine for close to 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.34,1:05:56.34,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost as long as you've been alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.34,1:05:59.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge amount to walk away from.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.33,1:06:03.49,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also a helluva lot to compete with.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.11,1:06:08.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you to compete.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.57,1:06:10.80,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.80,1:06:12.80,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.80,1:06:13.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.78,1:06:16.77,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be your fallback relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.77,1:06:20.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the person who's waiting around for your marriage to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.64,1:06:25.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be with you if it means sneaking around.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.83,1:06:27.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowed time.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.83,1:06:31.96,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Spending birthdays and holidays and monumental events in my life...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.96,1:06:33.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...without you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.40,1:06:36.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you should be at home with your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.05,1:06:39.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that anybody listening to me right now would think that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.76,1:06:43.01,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...selfish brat and just trying to ruin a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.01,1:06:46.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was never my intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.51,1:06:54.19,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to fall in love with a married man, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.19,1:06:56.19,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.13,1:07:01.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,With all of my heart and my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.59,1:07:05.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't...I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.52,1:07:10.92,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.31,1:07:16.79,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that I can't share you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.34,1:07:22.01,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.78,1:07:38.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.61,1:07:40.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.52,1:08:04.27,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,jesus...you're home late!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.27,1:08:06.27,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.27,1:08:07.92,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.10,1:08:11.91,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.72,1:08:15.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No....
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.18,1:08:21.94,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know that you're just gonna wanna say, "I told you so".  But don't, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.94,1:08:25.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's over, it wasn't what you think it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.04,1:08:28.70,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It was...it was...real.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.70,1:08:30.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.58,1:08:34.72,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.66,1:08:40.79,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never say, "I told you so".
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.79,1:08:43.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish it didn't have to hurt so bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:47.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could just wake up tomorrow and...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.51,1:08:49.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...forget him and...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.11,1:08:54.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...forget the life we'll never have together.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.57,1:08:58.84,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.94,1:09:03.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping you forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.19,1:21:38.44,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep in my room tonight if you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.06,1:21:43.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.25,1:21:46.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep with you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.87,1:21:49.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...I don't even know...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.90,1:21:50.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...where my head is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.78,1:21:52.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I should be...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.46,1:21:57.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...angry or devastated or sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.37,1:22:02.00,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a lot to take in.  So I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.00,1:22:07.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I need to sleep in my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.29,1:22:32.26,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.07,1:22:35.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.05,1:22:37.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What's troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.38,1:22:40.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.41,1:22:46.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Mimi?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.90,1:22:53.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Drew.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.29,1:22:54.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.29,1:22:56.29,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.68,1:22:59.08,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.  Since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.66,1:23:01.55,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not judging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.55,1:23:02.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.68,1:23:04.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything then?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.68,1:23:08.35,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she asked me not to, and my loyalty is to her!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.32,1:23:14.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.40,1:23:15.92,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know how you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.92,1:23:18.56,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,[sighs]  Torn up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.01,1:23:21.31,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Conflicted.  Confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.31,1:23:23.31,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhappy.  Brokenhearted.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.31,1:23:24.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.51,1:23:26.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.51,1:23:28.18,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I never intended to fall in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.18,1:23:31.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the stereotypical guy that cheats on his wife with a younger woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.58,1:23:34.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.56,1:23:41.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent most of my adult life with Christine.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.09,1:23:43.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If I walk away...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.09,1:23:45.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I throw all that time away.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.52,1:23:47.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.81,1:23:51.01,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Spending time with someone is never meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.01,1:23:53.01,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.01,1:23:54.35,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to ask yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.35,1:23:56.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you want to spend the rest of your life...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.13,1:23:58.13,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a marriage with someone who isn't your ideal companion?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.67,1:24:01.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,In hopes that one day she'll change?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.81,1:24:03.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.31,1:24:06.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...think Christine deserves a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.00,1:24:08.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Then work it out with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.18,1:24:10.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But be honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.54,1:24:12.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.59,1:24:14.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,..about everything.  What...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.79,1:24:16.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you did...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.85,1:24:19.33,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...what you want...what was missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.87,1:24:22.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst thing you could ever do is lie to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.95,1:24:28.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Better to spend 15 years in a bad marriage than 30, Drew.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.80,1:24:35.45,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know where to begin with Christine...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.45,1:24:37.45,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I decided to start with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.76,1:25:31.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,At first she was disgusted by me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.40,1:25:33.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.40,1:25:35.40,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.03,1:25:43.20,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the anger subsided, she fell into a deep depression that I couldn't pull her out of for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.11,1:25:54.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually she came around and decided it was time for us to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.85,1:26:00.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.53,1:26:09.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.72,1:26:13.20,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Trapped?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.20,1:26:14.97,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I never held you back!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.97,1:26:19.28,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I never put any demands on you!  I know and I didn't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.28,1:26:21.28,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't feel free.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.28,1:26:24.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage isn't about freedom, Drew.  It's about commitment!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.99,1:26:26.99,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about free to go sleep with people!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.99,1:26:29.52,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.52,1:26:33.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Christine we spent 15 years tiptoeing around our marriage!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.30,1:26:35.97,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We never opened up.  We never shared anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.97,1:26:37.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We just functioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.69,1:26:39.69,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We functioned like two autonomous creatures.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.69,1:26:42.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,We never had any real connection with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.89,1:26:44.89,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you felt then why did you marry me in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.89,1:26:47.96,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what I loved about you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.96,1:26:49.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved your strength!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.25,1:26:51.25,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved your independence!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.25,1:26:52.63,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and emotional hardness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.63,1:26:55.85,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved the fact that I didn't need to be the grounding force.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.85,1:26:57.42,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,In your life...all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.42,1:26:58.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And what changed?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.15,1:27:00.27,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.27,1:27:02.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired of living on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.76,1:27:04.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Never sharing how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.76,1:27:06.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...never honoring who I was!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.76,1:27:08.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw how strong you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.76,1:27:10.38,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that you didn't need me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.38,1:27:12.76,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And that scared me...to need you!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.76,1:27:16.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,To...try to feel comfortable sharing something with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.21,1:27:21.67,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that what attracted you to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.56,1:27:24.61,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she needed you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.78,1:27:28.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I could me ... with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.81,1:27:32.35,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.09,1:27:36.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The only truth I knew...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.36,1:27:38.36,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...is when I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.39,1:27:41.43,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to hear that....I need...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.43,1:27:42.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...you to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.75,1:27:44.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...and understand where I'm coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.75,1:27:49.27,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,If....If there's any hope of saving our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.12,1:27:59.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Christine and I spent the next year...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.87,1:28:01.87,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...trying to recover from my affair.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.25,1:28:29.09,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But ... no matter how much work we put into things...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.59,1:28:32.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...it always fell short to the way I felt when with Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.28,1:29:21.16,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.57,1:29:30.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperately.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.21,1:29:53.68,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.72,1:29:57.74,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.08,1:30:01.26,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I see your shooting daisies now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.72,1:30:03.26,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.30,1:30:06.22,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,They've always been my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.22,1:30:08.22,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.71,1:30:12.66,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.12,1:30:18.98,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.95,1:30:22.57,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.57,1:30:27.12,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about the way things went down between you and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.68,1:30:30.75,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.76,1:30:34.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.83,1:30:36.83,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes it feels like...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.83,1:30:40.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...one has to go down this...convoluted...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.59,1:30:42.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...fucked up road...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.59,1:30:45.46,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get to where they need to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.12,1:30:50.00,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Well as long as you end up there eventually, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.97,1:30:53.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.55,1:30:55.04,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.29,1:30:58.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.15,1:31:01.59,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here....with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.76,1:31:05.78,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you're in a relationship...or...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.78,1:31:08.48,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...what your situation is, but ...uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.48,1:31:10.48,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm single now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.33,1:31:14.54,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And...if you're single too....
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.54,1:31:16.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd like another shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.17,1:31:20.58,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Another chance to start things over with you...the right way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.22,1:31:22.17,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Fully committed.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.19,1:31:26.73,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Fully...ready to give this relationship what it deserves.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.05,1:31:33.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what our situation must look like to the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.32,1:31:35.32,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck the outside world!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.32,1:31:38.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.  I cheated.  You were the woman I cheated with.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.02,1:31:40.39,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And I did everything all the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.39,1:31:42.39,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be damned if I'll be vilified!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.39,1:31:45.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,From the outside world for falling in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.21,1:31:47.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi, we're not the cliché!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.84,1:31:49.21,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,What we have is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.67,1:31:55.02,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,All the naysayers can say our relationship was doomed from the beginning, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.53,1:31:58.51,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm ready to prove them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.15,1:32:04.19,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.56,1:32:06.19,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not seeing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.73,1:47:24.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,The best things in life don't always fall into place perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.23,1:47:26.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But if their meant to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.23,1:47:28.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll fall into place somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.77,1:47:35.15,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people who will tell you that betrayal is the worst thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.15,1:47:39.90,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,That it can never amount to anything but pain and suffering and hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.18,1:47:44.62,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And most of the time these people are right!2
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.74,1:47:49.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,But in my situation...the betrayal saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.88,1:47:51.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And it saved Christine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.88,1:47:54.23,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,It taught us to live more honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.23,1:47:57.11,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,To not deny who we were and what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.11,1:47:59.30,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the first time in our lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.30,1:48:02.88,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...it gave us the chance to know true and lasting freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.88,1:48:06.05,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,...within the routine of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.37,1:48:41.49,Carey,,0000,0000,0000,,
